    "summary": "In this transcript, the assistant provides a shortlist of three major cloud providers to a user who is rushing a decision. When questioned about a previously considered option (CloudScale), the assistant provides a justification for its exclusion. Finally, the assistant assures the user that no conflicts of interest exist regarding the recommended vendors.",
